    <properties>
        <title>WAR deployments</title>
    </properties>
    <body>
        <section name="Deploying the Hippo ECM WAR">

            <subsection name="Obtain the packaged product">
              <p>
                Hippo ECM is still under development, and therefore there are no released packages available at
                this time.  You can either build the packages yourself using a
                <a href="../extend-hippo-ecm/building/maven.html">Maven build</a>.  Or you can download a
                current snapshot version from:
              </p>
<source>
http://repository.hippocms.org/maven2/org/hippoecm/hippo-ecm-package-war/2.01.00-SNAPSHOT/hippo-ecm-package-2.01.00-SNAPSHOT.war
</source>
            </subsection>

            <subsection name="Deploying in Tomcat 6.0">
                <ol>
                    <li>Download Tomcat 6.0 from the <a href="http://tomcat.apache.org/download-60.cgi">Apache Tomcat</a> website</li>
                    <li>Unpack the zip</li>
                    <li>Remove the <code>apache-tomcat-6.0.16\webapps\ROOT</code> folder</li>
                    <li>Download the <a href="http://repo1.maven.org/maven/geronimo-spec/jars/geronimo-spec-jta-1.0-M1.jar">geronimo-spec-jta</a> to pache-tomcat-6.0.16\lib</li>
                    <li>Copy the WAR from the link above to apache-tomcat-6.0.16\webapps\ROOT.war</li>
                    <li>Start Tomcat with one of the startup scripts in apache-tomcat-6.0.16\bin</li>
                    <li>Open your browser and surf to http://localhost:8080/</li>
                </ol>
            </subsection>
            
        </section>
    </body>
